  "description": "Industrial / SCADA / HMI React components for Altara — waterfall spectrogram (FFT), OEE dashboard, PID tuning, alarm annunciator, multi-pen trend recorder, P&ID symbols, process flow diagram, motor dashboard, predictive-maintenance gauge for manufacturing, energy, and process-control HMIs.",
  "license": "MIT",
  "author": "Jaya Sai Kishan Chapparam",
